South African Mineworkers Union Declares Pay Dispute With Northam Platinum

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-12T14:20:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/south-african-mineworkers-union-declares-pay-dispute-with-northam-platinum.html
South Africa ’s National Union of
Mineworkers said it has declared a dispute with  Northam Platinum
Ltd. (NHM)  “over the company’s reluctance to bargain” over pay.  The labor union commented in a e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
